    - try_files for React Router (fallback to index.html)
    - gzip compression for js/css/html
    - cache headers: 1 year for /static/, no-cache for index.html
    - proxy /api/ requests to backend service (for docker-compose)
  EXPOSE 80
  HEALTHCHECK: wget -q --spider http://localhost/ || exit 1

Also generate: frontend/.dockerignore
